  <prompt>Implement IScheduledJob — nightly recon that scans source-of-truth lookups across all configured entities and reconciles vs `sprk_userentityassociation` rows. Upserts missing, deletes orphans. Reports ProcessedItems per run. Catches drift from non-BFF mutations (maker portal direct edits).</prompt>
  <goal>Real recon logic — not no-op. Registered in Spaarke.Scheduling. Visible/triggerable via /api/admin/jobs. Detects intentionally-introduced drift in integration test.</goal>
  <constraints>
    <constraint source="spec FR-2P2.7">Real logic (NOT no-op — Phase 2 in-scope per owner)</constraint>
    <constraint source="NFR-08">correlationId per run</constraint>
    <constraint source="bff-extensions.md §A">BFF pre-merge checklist</constraint>
  </constraints>
