  <steps>
    <step order="0">Context check + FR-2P2.7</step>
    <step order="1">Implement MembershipReconciliationJob : IScheduledJob</step>
    <step order="2">Reconcile per entity: source lookups + identity normalization → expected junction rows → diff against actual → upsert/delete</step>
    <step order="3">Report ProcessedItems = rowsTouched</step>
    <step order="4">Seed sprk_backgroundjob row with cron `0 2 * * *` (nightly 2AM UTC)</step>
    <step order="5">Unit tests: drift detection happy path + orphan removal + missing-row upsert</step>
    <step order="6">Integration test: introduce drift in junction table → run job → verify reconciled</step>
  </steps>
  <acceptance-criteria>
